title: CBS Cancels Extant " But There's Good News for Halle Berry - Burlington Times News
text:
CBS has canceled its summer sci-fi drama Extant , which starred Berry as an astronaut who returns from space pregnant with an alien baby, after two seasons, TVGuide.com has confirmed. However, Berry doesn't seem to be too sad letting the show go."
